OL,3,CTroubles investigation body receives
OL,4,C85 enquiries
OL,6,FA new body tasked with investigating
OL,7,Foutstanding cases from the Northern
OL,8,FIreland Troubles has registered 85
OL,9,Fenquiries since becoming operational
OL,10,Fearlier this year.
OL,12,FThe Independent Commission for
OL,13,FReconciliation and Information (ICRIR)
OL,14,Fwas created by the previous
OL,15,Fgovernment's controversial Legacy Act
OL,16,Fwhich halted scores of civil
OL,17,Flitigation and inquests into Troubles
OL,18,Fdeaths.
