OL,6,FBereaved families, victims and certain
OL,7,Fpublic authorities can instead request
OL,8,Fthe ICRIR carry out an investigation.
OL,10,FHowever, opposition to the new
OL,11,Fcommission led to protests and claims
OL,12,Fthat access to justice had been shut
OL,13,Fdown.
OL,15,FThe ICRIR announced on Monday that
OL,16,Fsince becoming operational in May, it
OL,17,Fhas registered 85 enquiries from
OL,18,Fvictims, survivors and families about
OL,19,Fthe possibility of an investigation
OL,20,Finto their injury or the death of a
OL,21,Floved one.
