OL,6,FIn an update to its work, the ICRIR
OL,7,Falso confirmed that of those
OL,8,Fenquiries, eight have been accepted
OL,9,Ffor investigation and are in the
OL,10,FInformation Recovery stage.
OL,12,FThe body is led by retired judge Sir
OL,13,FDeclan Morgan, a former lord chief
OL,14,Fjustice for Northern Ireland.
OL,16,FThe Chief Commissioner said the update
OL,17,F"reflects the commission's values
OL,18,Fabout being open and accountable, and
OL,19,Fabove all the focus on delivering for
OL,20,Fthose who have come to the commission
OL,21,Fseeking answers."
