OL,6,FSir Declan said that all at the
OL,7,Fcommission were committed to following
OL,8,Fthe approach that the Design Framework
OL,9,Fsets out so the body meets what it has
OL,10,Fpromised.
OL,12,F"We are now at a stage where people
OL,13,Fhave come forward and put their trust
OL,14,Fin the commission to take their
OL,15,Frequests forward. We will now do so in
OL,16,Fline with our values and core
OL,17,Fprinciples," he said.
OL,19,F"We are moving into the next phase of
OL,20,Four work as the serious and important
OL,21,Ftask of investigation begins.
