OL,6,F"In doing this we must meet the
OL,7,Fcommitments that we have made to each
OL,8,Fperson who comes to us, through our
OL,9,Fopen and published policies, and
OL,10,Fthrough our trauma and resiliency
OL,11,Finformed model."
OL,13,FCommissioner for investigations Peter
OL,14,FSheridan added: "Many of the
OL,15,Findividuals and families that the
OL,16,Fcommission will meet will have
OL,17,Fexperienced harm and suffering and may
OL,18,Fhave waited many years to find out
OL,19,Fmore about what they and their loved
OL,20,Fones went through.
